                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100919-18-off96 t18100919-18-cd97"></join>, two gowns, value 20 s. a cloak, value 20 s. a shawl, value 15 s. a cap, value 1 d. a bonnet, value 15 s. a laced cloak, value 30 s. a spencer, value 1 s. and five yards of muslin, value 50 s. the property of 
                     
