            . I am the wife of the prosecutor, he is a housekeeper, he <rs id="t18100919-18-viclabel98" type="occupation">keeps the <placeName id="t18100919-18-crimeloc99">Cooper's Arms public house</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18100919-18-crimeloc99" type="placeName" value="Cooper's Arms public house"></interp>
