                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100919-18-off96 t18100919-18-crimeloc99"></join>
                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100919-18-victim193 t18100919-18-viclabel98"></join>. The prisoner left my service on the 8th of August, between eight and nine in the evening; I missed the things that same nigh; I saw her the next evening at the Flying-horse, Lambeth-street, Whitechapel; she had my gown and spencer on her back; she took the property out of the one pair of stairs room.</p>
               <p>Q. When was the last time you had seen them before they were stolen - A. On the 7th of August.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18100919-18-person195">
                  ELIZABETH 
                  ALLINGHAM
               <interp inst="t18100919-18-person195" type="surname" value="ALLINGHAM"></interp>
